{"hierarchy":{"paths":[["doc:\/\/OUDSThemesOrange\/documentation\/OUDSThemesOrange","doc:\/\/OUDSThemesOrange\/documentation\/OUDSThemesOrange\/OrangeThemeControlItemComponentTokensProvider"]]},"abstract":[{"text":"Provider of dimension semantic tokens to use for control-item-layout-based dimensions","type":"text"}],"sections":[],"metadata":{"modules":[{"name":"Theme Orange"}],"roleHeading":"Instance Property","role":"symbol","title":"dimensions","symbolKind":"property","fragments":[{"text":"let","kind":"keyword"},{"text":" ","kind":"text"},{"text":"dimensions","kind":"identifier"},{"text":": any ","kind":"text"},{"text":"AllDimensionSemanticTokensProvider","preciseIdentifier":"s:18OUDSThemesContract34AllDimensionSemanticTokensProviderP","kind":"typeIdentifier"}],"externalID":"s:16OUDSThemesOrange0B39ThemeControlItemComponentTokensProviderC10dimensions0A8Contract020AllDimensionSemanticgH0_pvp"},"schemaVersion":{"patch":0,"major":0,"minor":3},"identifier":{"interfaceLanguage":"swift","url":"doc:\/\/OUDSThemesOrange\/documentation\/OUDSThemesOrange\/OrangeThemeControlItemComponentTokensProvider\/dimensions"},"variants":[{"traits":[{"interfaceLanguage":"swift"}],"paths":["\/documentation\/oudsthemesorange\/orangethemecontrolitemcomponenttokensprovider\/dimensions"]}],"primaryContentSections":[{"kind":"declarations","declarations":[{"languages":["swift"],"tokens":[{"text":"let","kind":"keyword"},{"text":" ","kind":"text"},{"text":"dimensions","kind":"identifier"},{"text":": any ","kind":"text"},{"text":"AllDimensionSemanticTokensProvider","preciseIdentifier":"s:18OUDSThemesContract34AllDimensionSemanticTokensProviderP","kind":"typeIdentifier","identifier":"doc:\/\/OUDSThemesContract\/documentation\/OUDSThemesContract\/AllDimensionSemanticTokensProvider"}],"platforms":["macOS"]}]}],"kind":"symbol","references":{"ic_theme_orange.png":{"alt":null,"variants":[{"url":"\/images\/OUDSThemesOrange\/ic_theme_orange.png","traits":["1x","light"]}],"identifier":"ic_theme_orange.png","type":"image"},"doc://OUDSThemesOrange/documentation/OUDSThemesOrange/OrangeThemeControlItemComponentTokensProvider":{"abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"A class which wraps all "},{"type":"strong","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"component  tokens"}]},{"type":"text","text":" for components with a "},{"type":"emphasis","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"control item"}]},{"type":"text","text":" layout like "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"OUDSSwitch"},{"type":"text","text":", "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"OUDSRadioButton"},{"type":"text","text":" and "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"OUDSCheckboItem"},{"type":"text","text":"."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"Contains also references to semantic tokens providers so as to be able to use them to define the component tokens."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"This provider should be integrated as a "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"AllControlItemComponentTokensProvider"},{"type":"text","text":" implementation inside "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"OUDSTheme"},{"type":"text","text":" so as to provide"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"all tokens to the users. It helps users to override some of the tokens and assign them to an "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"OUDSTheme"},{"type":"text","text":" implementation to use."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"Custom themes can use subclass of "},{"identifier":"doc:\/\/OUDSThemesOrange\/documentation\/OUDSThemesOrange\/OrangeThemeControlItemComponentTokensProvider","isActive":true,"type":"reference"},{"type":"text","text":" and apply the provider they need."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"It implements also the protocol "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"ControlItemComponentTokens"},{"type":"text","text":" so as to expose the component tokens for control-item-layout-basded components through any "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"OUDSTheme"},{"type":"text","text":"."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"Such components tokens are defined with raw and semantic tokens of sizes (from "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"SizeSemanticTokensProvider"},{"type":"text","text":"),"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"borders (from "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"AllBorderSemanticTokensProvider"},{"type":"text","text":"),  colors (from "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"AllColorSemanticTokensProvider"},{"type":"text","text":")  and spaces (from "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"AllSpaceSemanticTokensProvider"},{"type":"text","text":")."}],"fragments":[{"kind":"keyword","text":"class"},{"kind":"text","text":" "},{"kind":"identifier","text":"OrangeThemeControlItemComponentTokensProvider"}],"url":"\/documentation\/oudsthemesorange\/orangethemecontrolitemcomponenttokensprovider","identifier":"doc:\/\/OUDSThemesOrange\/documentation\/OUDSThemesOrange\/OrangeThemeControlItemComponentTokensProvider","navigatorTitle":[{"kind":"identifier","text":"OrangeThemeControlItemComponentTokensProvider"}],"type":"topic","kind":"symbol","title":"OrangeThemeControlItemComponentTokensProvider","role":"symbol"},"doc://OUDSThemesOrange/documentation/OUDSThemesOrange/OrangeThemeControlItemComponentTokensProvider/dimensions":{"role":"symbol","title":"dimensions","url":"\/documentation\/oudsthemesorange\/orangethemecontrolitemcomponenttokensprovider\/dimensions","abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"Provider of dimension semantic tokens to use for control-item-layout-based dimensions"}],"type":"topic","identifier":"doc:\/\/OUDSThemesOrange\/documentation\/OUDSThemesOrange\/OrangeThemeControlItemComponentTokensProvider\/dimensions","kind":"symbol","fragments":[{"kind":"keyword","text":"let"},{"kind":"text","text":" "},{"kind":"identifier","text":"dimensions"},{"kind":"text","text":": any "},{"preciseIdentifier":"s:18OUDSThemesContract34AllDimensionSemanticTokensProviderP","kind":"typeIdentifier","text":"AllDimensionSemanticTokensProvider"}]},"doc://OUDSThemesContract/documentation/OUDSThemesContract/AllDimensionSemanticTokensProvider":{"abstract":[{"text":"Something which provides all semantic tokens of _","type":"text"}],"fragments":[{"text":"protocol","kind":"keyword"},{"text":" ","kind":"text"},{"text":"AllDimensionSemanticTokensProvider","kind":"identifier"}],"url":"\/documentation\/oudsthemescontract\/alldimensionsemantictokensprovider","identifier":"doc:\/\/OUDSThemesContract\/documentation\/OUDSThemesContract\/AllDimensionSemanticTokensProvider","navigatorTitle":[{"text":"AllDimensionSemanticTokensProvider","kind":"identifier"}],"type":"topic","kind":"symbol","title":"AllDimensionSemanticTokensProvider","role":"symbol"},"doc://OUDSThemesOrange/documentation/OUDSThemesOrange":{"url":"\/documentation\/oudsthemesorange","type":"topic","role":"collection","kind":"symbol","identifier":"doc:\/\/OUDSThemesOrange\/documentation\/OUDSThemesOrange","images":[{"identifier":"ic_theme_orange.png","type":"icon"}],"abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"The Orange theme overrides some tokens from the basic "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"OUDSTheme"},{"type":"text","text":" and should be seen as the default theme for the OUDS library with the Orange brand colors for example."}],"title":"Theme Orange"}}}